    <note>Song(2) Shou [1575] He passed an initial decree examination at age 15, and then again in 1008 at age 17. Changyan's [1556] uncle, Minqiu's [1571] father, Hui's [1568] great grandfather. The daughter of his niece, who was the wife of the imperial clansman Zhao(1) Shien [3209] {great great grandson of Zhao(1) Taizu [9001]}, married Song(2) Anguo [3788] (of the Kaifeng, Yongqiu Song and, by process of elimination, Song(2) Xiang's [8119] son), Bi(1) Shian's [8107] son-in-law. Fan Zuyu. WJ. 51.5a. XCB, 92.6a; LPJ, 7.8b; SS, 291.6b-7a; Du Dagui, 'xia,' 8.5b. CBD, 1, 753.</note>
